thread.title: Liberty's Gunner Anglovich is Week 6 EPC offensive MVP
thread.title_full: Liberty's Gunner Anglovich is Week 6 EPC offensive MVP

title: Liberty's Gunner Anglovich is Week 6 EPC offensive MVP
text:
Gunner Anglovich , Liberty Gunner Anglovich (lehighvalleylive.com file photo) 
The junior running back helped the Hurricanes run for more than 300 yards Friday night, a big factor in their 41-34 win over Parkland . 
Anglovich took 17 carries for 154 yards and two touchdowns, including a 75-yard score. For the season, he now has 71 rushes for 450 yards and six touchdowns.
